            "content_html": "<h1>一些支付卡推荐和记录</h1>\n<!--\n * @?: *********************************************************************\n * @Author: Weidows\n * @LastEditors: Weidows\n * @LastEditTime: 2024-09-04 03:06:52\n * @FilePath: \\Blog-private\\source\\_posts\\life\\shopping\\card.md\n * @Description:\n * @:\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡏⠻⣄\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⣀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣀⡾⠀⠀⣿\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣠⡶⠟⠛⠉⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠉⠛⠻⠿⣤⣀⣠⡴⠋\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣴⠟⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣤⠂⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⢶⣀\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⡾⠉⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡴⠁⠀⠀⠀⡞⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠳⣄\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣴⠋⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢠⠏⠀⠀⠀⠀⡾⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢰⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⢷⡀\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⠃⠀⠀⠀⠀⢰⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⣄\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⣀⣿⢠⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣶⠀⣧⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⣆\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼⠁⠀⣰⠀⠀⠀⠀⣾⢸⣿⣀⣤⣶⡛⠁⣿⠘⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⠀⠀⣿⠀⢻⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠸\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⠀⠀⡟⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⡈⡏⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⡜⡄⢿⠀⠀⠀⠀⣾⣧⣾⢸⠀⢸⠀⠀⡇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡇\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⡇⠀⠀⣇⠀⠀⠀⠀⣷⣿⣿⣶⣦⣀⠀⠀⠀⠹⡘⣿⡀⠀⠀⢹⣿⠃⢸⠀⣿⠀⢠⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣄⣧\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼⠀⠀⠀⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⢿⠉⠉⠉⠻⣿⣷⡀⠀⠀⠈⠁⠙⢦⣀⣸⠋⠈⣸⣼⢻⠀⣾⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⢸⣿\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⠀⣿⠀⠸⡄⣤⠀⠀⠀⣧⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠀⠀⣿⣿⠇⠀⠀⠀⠀⣾⢸⣿\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢰⡇⠀⣿⠀⠀⠙⠿⣿⠛⠒⠛⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣾⣿⣿⣿⣿⣦⡀⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⣿⣿\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⠀⣴⠋⠙⣦⠀⠀⠀⣇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼⠉⠙⠳⠦⣤⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠻⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⣿⣿\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⢤⠇⣀⡀⣼⠀⠀⠀⢹⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⢰⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⠟⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢠⣯⣿⣿\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⣠⠋⣠⠟⠁⠀⠈⠛⣄⠀⠀⠀⣇⠀⠀⠀⠀⢹⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⠟⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢾⣁⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⣾⣤⡏⠉⠉⣿\n * ⠀⠀⢀⣞⠤⣴⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣧⠀⠀⢿⠉⠳⣤⡀⠀⠁⠀⠠⠶⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠉⠧⣴⣾⣿⣿⠟⡇⠀⠀⢸\n * ⣠⠚⠁⢀⠏⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠸⡀⠀⠈⡏⠛⠶⣤⡉⠛⠶⢤⣤⣀⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣀⡴⣿⣿⠟⠁⠀⠀⡇⠀⠀⢸\n * ⠀⠀⠀⢸⠀⠘⡄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢹⠀⡿⡄⠀⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⠲⣤⡀⠙⢦⠉⠉⠉⠉⠉⠉⠁⠀⠀⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡇⠀⠀⢸\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠘⡄⠀⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣸⠛⡄⢻⠀⠸⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠛⢦⡉⢦⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⢰⠇⠀⠀⢸\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⢿⠀⠈⠙⢦⣄⣠⠴⠃⢠⠃⠀⡇⠀⣇⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⢾⣦⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣿⠀⠀⠀⠀⣼⠀⠀⠀⠀⡇\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠙⢤⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡴⠋⠀⠀⡇⠀⢿⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠈⠳⣄⠀⠀⠀⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⡇\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢀⡇⠀⠘⣿⣿⣄⡀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠳⠀⠀⡇⠀⠀⠀⢰⠁⠀⠀⠀⠀⡇\n * ⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⡾⠀⠀⠀⣿⣿⣿⣿⣷⣶⣶⣤⣄⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⢸⠁⠀⠀⠀⡿⠀⠀⠀⠀⠀⣷\n *\n * @!: *********************************************************************\n-->\n<blockquote class=\"pullquote mindmap mindmap-sm\"><ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E5%8D%A1%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90%E5%92%8C%E8%AE%B0%E5%BD%95\">一些支付卡推荐和记录</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E8%99%9A%E6%8B%9F%E4%BF%A1%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%A1-virtual-card\">虚拟信用卡-virtual-card</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E7%9A%AE%E5%8D%A1%E5%AE%9D\">皮卡宝</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%80%9F%E7%89%A9%E8%A1%A8\">借物表</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</blockquote>\n<p><a><img src= \"https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/img/loading.svg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/img/divider.png\" alt=\"分割线\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"虚拟信用卡-virtual-card\">虚拟信用卡-virtual-card</h2>\n<p>毕竟我用在国外支付的需求不多, 金额也不大, 不少可以用 PayPal 绑国内储蓄卡, 所以我的需求如下</p>\n<ol>\n<li>免月费/年费</li>\n<li>免 KYC (实名认证)</li>\n<li>可以接受高费率, 但开卡费尽可能低</li>\n<li>尽可能能通过 RMB/USDT 充值</li>\n<li>最低充值限额尽可能低</li>\n<li>不求支持场景非常多吧, 但尽量别是比较差的卡 bin, 常用的平台稳定就行</li>\n</ol>\n<p>找了一圈 (Depay, FomePay, FomeCard, 飞扬, globalcash, vcc.agency, 还有 TG 上其他开卡机器人), 我用到的会在下面用标题记下来</p>\n<h3 id=\"皮卡宝\">皮卡宝</h3>\n<p>TG 上的, 开卡费 <code>5$</code>, 充值最低 <code>20$</code> (只能充 U)</p>\n<p>安全性看起来还不错 (有客户群, 客服一直活跃, 老板买了好多 TG 优质号码)</p>\n<p>能绑国内平台支付(虽然用起来得换区)</p>\n<p>我刚用时费率 5%, 最近降到了 4% (无 KYC 下最常见的费率了)</p>\n<p><img src= \"https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/img/loading.svg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/blog/photo_2024-08-27_17-41-55.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><img src= \"https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/img/loading.svg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/blog/photo_2024-08-27_17-41-57.jpg\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><a><img src= \"https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/img/loading.svg\" data-lazy-src=\"https://pan.weidows.tech/d/local/img/divider.png\" alt=\"分割线\"></a></p>\n<h2 id=\"借物表\">借物表</h2>\n<p>暂无.</p>\n<script type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"https://unpkg.com/kity@2.0.4/dist/kity.min.js\"></script><script type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"https://unpkg.com/kityminder-core@1.4.50/dist/kityminder.core.min.js\"></script><script type=\"text&#x2F;javascript\" src=\"/mindmap/mindmap.js\"></script><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text&#x2F;css\" href=\"/mindmap/mindmap.css\">",
            "tags": [
                "card"
            ]
